General.Name: Energiedienst Holding AG
General.GicIndustry: Independent Power and Renewable Electricity Producers
General.Description: Energiedienst Holding AG, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the production, distribution, and sale of electricity under NatureEnergie brand in Switzerland. It generates electricity from hydro, gas, sun, and wind sources. The company also provides heating solutions; car sharing with electric cars; and plans, installs, and implements photovoltaic systems for private customers. It serves commercial customers, such as housing associations, as well as district concepts, heating networks, and services for municipalities. The company was founded in 1998 and is based in Laufenburg, Switzerland. Energiedienst Holding AG is a subsidiary of EnBW Energie Baden-Württemberg AG.
